# TextInput — Styles

CSS file: `@acko/css/text-input.css`

## CSS Classes

### Structure
- `.acko-text-input` — flex column wrapper, `gap: 4px`
- `.acko-text-input-label` — label-lg typography tokens
- `.acko-text-input-wrapper` — flex row, border, rounded-full
- `.acko-text-input-el` — the actual `<input>` element

### Sizes (via `.acko-text-input-wrapper-{size}`)
| Size | Height | Padding | Font | Icon size |
|------|--------|---------|------|-----------|
| sm | `40px` (h-40) | px-16 | `--font-body-sm-size` | `--font-body-sm-size` |
| md | `48px` (h-48) | px-20 | `--font-body-md-size` | `--font-body-md-size` |
| lg | `56px` (h-56) | px-24 | `--font-body-lg-size` | `--font-body-lg-size` |

### Variants / Children
- `.acko-text-input-icon-left` / `.acko-text-input-icon-right` — icon slots, sized to match the size variant's font token
- `.acko-text-input-prefix` / `.acko-text-input-suffix` — text addons
- `.acko-text-input-helper-text` / `.acko-text-input-error-text` — below input
- `.acko-text-input-char-count` — right-aligned character count
- `.acko-text-input-required` — red asterisk

### States (raw CSS)

| State | Border | Background | Label | Icon | Extra |
|-------|--------|-----------|-------|------|-------|
| Default | `--color-input-border` (`grey-150` light / `grey-600` dark) | `--color-input-bg` (`grey-white` light / `grey-750` dark) | `--color-text-default` | `--color-text-secondary` | — |
| Hover | `--color-input-hover-border` (`grey-200` light / `grey-550` dark) | `--color-input-bg` | unchanged | unchanged | Pointer devices only (`@media hover:hover`) |
| `.acko-text-input-focused` | `--color-input-focus-border` (`grey-200`) + `box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--color-input-focus-ring)` (`grey-150` light / `grey-600` dark) | `--color-input-bg` | `--color-primary` | `--color-primary` | Placeholder fades to `--color-text-disabled` (200ms ease) |
| `.acko-text-input-filled` | `--color-input-filled-border` (`grey-200` light / `grey-550` dark) — when value.length > 0, not focused | `--color-input-bg` | `--color-text-default` | `--color-text-secondary` | — |
| `.acko-text-input-error` | Gradient border `linear-gradient(0deg, red-200, grey-150)` via padding-box/border-box (dark: red-800 → grey-600) | `--color-input-bg` | `--color-text-default` (label does NOT turn red) | `--color-text-secondary` | `animation: acko-text-input-shake 300ms ease-out`; only helper/error text below changes color |
| `.acko-text-input-success` | `--color-input-hover-border` | `--color-input-bg` | `--color-text-default` | `--color-success` checkmark (dark: `--color-success-text`) | Replaces `iconRight`; inline SVG `Check` icon, `strokeWidth: 2.5`; `animation: acko-text-input-check-pop 300ms ease-out` |
| `.acko-text-input-disabled` | `--color-input-disabled-border` (`grey-150` light / `grey-600` dark) | `--color-input-disabled-bg` (`grey-100` light / `grey-700` dark) | `--color-text-secondary` | `--color-text-disabled` | `cursor: not-allowed` |
| `.acko-text-input-readonly` | `--color-border-subtle` | `--color-surface-raised` | `--color-text-default` | `--color-text-secondary` | Input text: `--color-text-supporting` |

### Character Count
- Displayed when `maxLength` prop is set
- Format: `{current}/{max}`
- Font: `--font-caption-size`, color `--color-text-secondary`, right-aligned

### Transition Timing
All border/background/shadow transitions use `200ms ease`.

### Border Consistency Rule
All input field borders follow the `--color-input-*` token family:
- Default: `--color-input-border` (`grey-150` light / `grey-600` dark)
- Hover: `--color-input-hover-border` (`grey-200` light / `grey-550` dark)
- Filled: `--color-input-filled-border` (`grey-200` light / `grey-550` dark)
- Focus: `--color-input-focus-border` (`grey-200`) + `box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--color-input-focus-ring)` (`grey-150` light / `grey-600` dark) — error fields excluded
This ensures visual consistency across all input components (TextInput, Textarea, InputGroup, Dropdown, OtpInput).

### Dark Theme Overrides
Scoped under `[data-theme="dark"]`:
- Default wrapper: bg `--color-input-bg` (`grey-750`), border `--color-input-border` (`grey-600`)
- Filled: border `--color-input-filled-border` (`grey-550`)
- Focus: border `--color-input-focus-border` + `box-shadow: 0 0 0 2px var(--color-input-focus-ring)` (`grey-600`)
- Disabled: bg `--color-input-disabled-bg` (`grey-700`), border `--color-input-disabled-border` (`grey-600`)
- Error border: gradient `linear-gradient(0deg, red-800, grey-600)`
- Success icon: `--color-success`
